rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Haruru became an Invidian citizen just so
I could see the Saffronia Tree every day, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But... there are a lot of rough people in Invidia,
and your status as a noble or mercenary
really matters, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0003
rows.name:
After living here, I realized it wasn't a very
comfortable city for Haruru, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I think I want to move to the more sophisticated
Superbia, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0005
rows.name:
But since I've already become an Invidian citizen,
I can't get permission... mo.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0006
rows.name:
The Empire will treat me as a spy no matter
what... mo.
